                          "fill": "#94A3B8",
                          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                          "width": "fill_container",
                          "content": "The present invention provides an adaptive compression system that dynamically adjusts encoding parameters based on real-time network metrics, achieving 40–60% bandwidth efficiency improvements over prior art.",
