                          "fill": "#94A3B8",
                          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                          "width": "fill_container",
                          "content": "1. A computer-implemented method for adaptive data compression, comprising:\n    receiving, by a processor, a data stream from a network interface;\n    monitoring network bandwidth conditions in real-time;\n    dynamically selecting a compression algorithm from a plurality of algorithms;\n    encoding the data stream using the selected algorithm.\n\n2. The method of claim 1, wherein dynamically selecting comprises applying a neural network model trained on historical bandwidth data.\n\n3. A system comprising: a processor; and a non-transitory memory storing instructions...",
